comments: This professor may not have much experience with online class, but response time is key when teaching an online class. Does not respond and takes days to respond. The book is hard to read and definitely needs reconsideration to make the materials more creative and keeps your attention. I got an A, but it is not about an A. I learned nothing

She is smart, good humored and always has an example to make the conceptualizations realistic. Very knowledgeable with theory of techniques and is an excellent teacher. Everything learned in her class could be used immediately in the clinical setting. Take this class.
